# Phase 2 populates this directory with numbered migration files:
#   001_init.sql               — observations, observation_runs, noise_counters
#   002_add_indexes.sql        — OBS-05 retention/compaction support
#   003_user_ips.sql (phase 4) — FW-08 belt-and-suspenders user↔IP mirror
#
# Phase 1 ships the directory with only this .gitkeep so the //go:embed
# migrations directive compiles (an empty directory on disk with no
# tracked files is invisible to git and breaks the build).
